  "text": "Let \u2202 V denote a Killing vector of the metric g \u00b5\u03bd dx \u00b5 dx \u03bd . Performing a Tduality along \u03be with the T-dual circle being parametrized by\u03be, subsequently shifting V \u2192 V + \u03b3\u03be and performing a second T-duality along\u03be leads to the following solution of type IIB supergravity which in Einstein frame reads [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] ",
